**v0.1.0**

- Mission-centric architecture refacto
- Core system: mission.ts, runner.ts, session.ts
- Mission commands: create, attach, detach, status
- Centralized UI library with color-coded output
- Type definitions for manifests and module results
- Storage abstraction layer

**v0.0.2**

- Fix netree module import issues
- Nine can now use -nt or --netree

**v0.0.1**

- Initial release
- IP scanner with subnet resolution
- Port status detection (open/forwarded/closed)
- Service version detection
- Color-coded terminal output
- Automatic report generation to ./loot/
- Global install via install.ts
